title: Largest rowi kiwi transfer (Department of Conservation of New Zealand)
text: ( Source : Department of Conservation of New Zealand ) Rowi The year-old chicks were returned to the forest today, bringing the population to between 400 and 500 rowi. It's the most rowi transferred on a single day and is a critical milestone
